  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bbf\u00a0\u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a \u0bae\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0ba4 \u0b89\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba3\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Radhika Kumaraswamy appointed member of the International Committee on Human Rights Experts on Ethiopia",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Radhika Kumaraswamy, a Sri Lankan national, has been appointed a member of the International Committee of the Red Cross (ICRC) on Ethiopia, UN Human Rights Council President Federico Willegas (28) announced on Tuesday.",
        "Radhika Kumaraswamy from Sri Lanka has been appointed as the third member of the panel, following the appointment of Kari Perry Murungi from Kenya and Steven Rurner from the United States last March (2).",
        "The appointment follows the resignation of Ferro Benzuda, a member of the committee, last (8) years.",
        "An international panel of human rights experts was set up by the UN Human Rights Council on December 17, 2021 to investigate international human rights abuses, humanitarian and refugee abuses in Ethiopia since November 2020.",
        "Radhika Kumaraswamy has many years of experience as a human rights lawyer and has held various important positions in Sri Lanka and internationally."
      ],
